msg: resource watcher changes (boolean to not start it if not already started)
Component.WrapModel introduced which wraps around an I(Compound)Model so that
the model of the component is right (getModelObject() and getModel().getObject(null) will return the same thing)
now getModelObject() always just does model.getObject(null) don't know if we always can do that, for example our feedbackmessage model did need a wrap around its model..
